@@TJvSoundValue.Balance
Summary
  Specifies the balance between the left and right volume of a device.
Description
  Use Balance to find or set the balance between the left and right volume. The value for this
  property must be a number from 0 (only right) to 100 (only left).
  
  Use <LINK TJvSoundControl.LastError, LastError> to determine if the operation was successful.
See Also
  TJvSoundValue.Volume

