@@TJvSoundControl.Create
Summary
  Creates and initializes an instance of TJvSoundControl.
Description
  Call \Create to create an instance of TJvSoundControl at runtime. A TJvSoundControl component
  placed on a form at design time is created automatically.
  
  Pass a single Component as a parameter to provide the control with an Owner that is responsible for
  freeing it.
Parameters
  AOwner - The owner for the instance of TJvSoundControl.
See Also
  TJvSoundControl.Destroy

